Acceptance: Durable versioned routes support Room-first and direct Session destinations, Item/Repo/Org selector, baseline event/repository filter, off-summary-threaded comments, independent action capabilities, enabled state, revision, provenance, indexes, and optimistic concurrency. The store permits at most one active route for each destination plus canonical selector; creation, update, restore, and concurrent writes either reject a collision transactionally or apply one documented deterministic winner. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.